    <descript>
      <abstract>This polygon layer represents the approximate size and location of parcels located within Prince William County, VA</abstract>
      <purpose>This is to be used for data analysis and cartographic overlay. This layer is used by multiple Prince William County applications such as County Mapper, Demographic Mapper, GPIN Centered Map and also for internal mapping projects.</purpose>
      <supplinf>Parcels (Ownership and recordation information is not included in digital data orders, but can be purchased seperately from the Office of Real Estate Assessments).</supplinf>
    </descript>

    <logic>Data is represented within the National Map Accuracy Standards. Original planimetric map data was provided at a scale of 1:2400. Parcels were recompiled, in accordance with National Map Accuracy Standards, from
source materials with varying levels of accuracy. Source was coded with each parcel and parcels are upgraded, as a more reliable source became available.
</logic>
